{
  "stem": "3605.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were even some newborn babies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were lying in long pillows on the podium there, where the cantor used to sing-- crying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was nothing to give them to help them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And outside were the German soldiers, sitting around a campfire, in the Werkshuhtz, singing holiday songs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a couple of the soldiers came in, and they picked up the babies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took the babies, and they threw them in the fire, singing heilige nacht-- holy night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wonder where God was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They thought that there is not going to be a witness to the cruelty, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] because we were all destined to die.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The 500 people were destined to die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But in the middle of the night, two Germans came in and called out two names-- my name, and another name.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When you hear a German call your name, you don't want to admit it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But somebody said, Jadzia, they are calling your name!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I was in trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I want to make a point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Before I was caught, that day, in between, I-- when my father was deported, I lived with a bunch of young people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were all Zionist-minded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they were-- and they kind of supported me in many ways there, being as I was illegal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were working in the glass factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in that whole place, very few women were legal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were 95% men to 5% woman, so I was illegal and a very rare thing, there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they all had kind of an allegiance to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They lost their mothers, and they lost their sisters, and they lost their wives.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was kind of the image of their lost relatives.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
